00:48:08.519 --> 00:48:16.079
cleaner. I want to be clean. Because cleaner is not good enough. You can have something

00:48:16.079 --> 00:48:21.399
that's really dirty and you can just dust it off with a hanky, with something else.

00:48:21.399 --> 00:48:28.159
Just let me dust that thing off. And here you go. It's cleaner, but it is not clean.

00:48:28.159 --> 00:48:34.319
Creating me a clean heart. Oh, that God would do a work in our hearts. Help us to be prepared.

00:48:34.319 --> 00:48:38.599
Break up your fallow ground. Lord, we love You. We thank You for loving us. We thank

00:48:38.599 --> 00:48:43.839
You for the Word. Lord, as we consider the indictment tonight, it reveals to us that

00:48:43.839 --> 00:48:51.679
You know. God, I don't know all that's taking place in the lives of these that are gathered

00:48:51.679 --> 00:49:01.919
tonight. But God, I know that You do. You know each of us. You know everything about

00:49:01.919 --> 00:49:10.199
us. God, if there's any sin in our lives, would You help us to deal with it? God, if

00:49:10.199 --> 00:49:21.919
there's maybe even some of the sin that we mention by name this evening. Sin that some

00:49:21.919 --> 00:49:27.199
would categorize as being big sin and others that would categorize as being little sin.

00:49:27.199 --> 00:49:33.339
Lord, help us not to have those categories, but help us to understand that sin is an offense

00:49:33.339 --> 00:49:41.139
against Thee as a holy God. And help us to be clean. Lord, do a work in us. Help us to

00:49:41.139 --> 00:49:46.380
do business with You. Help us not to quench and grieve the Holy Spirit. Help us to follow

00:49:46.380 --> 00:49:55.459
the instruction. To break up our fallow ground, to seek You with our whole heart. Lord, I

00:49:55.459 --> 00:50:00.139
pray that You'd move and work as only You can. And we'll give You the glory for it's

00:50:00.139 --> 00:50:00.659
in Christ.

00:50:00.659 --> 00:50:01.659
In Jesus' name we pray.

00:50:01.659 --> 00:50:02.979
Would you stand with me?

00:50:02.979 --> 00:50:04.179
Heads are bowed, eyes are closed.

